data.value:
What: The software is used for lock screen automatically when you left your work place Background: If you left your work place and your computer screen still is open, everyone can operate your computer, it is very dangerous How to use it? 1. Pair your bluetooth(such as phone, watch) with your computer 2. Input your paird bluetooth name 3. Click start button
Note: bluetooth must open all the time
